'The rider has the right to request and attend the analysis of the B sample. In accordance with the UCI anti-doping rules, the rider has been provisionally suspended until the adjudication of the affair.

'At this stage of the procedure, the UCI will not comment any further.'

The news comes in the week the Cycling Independent Reform Commission published its report into doping.

 

